      "id": "html-body",
      "type": "html",
      "content": "<div class=\"min-h-screen\">\r\n      \r\n      <section class=\"bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-50 to-white py-20 border-b border-gray-200\">\r\n        <div class=\"container max-w-4xl text-center\">\r\n          <h1 class=\"text-5xl font-bold mb-6\">About ObjectWire</h1>\r\n          <p class=\"text-xl text-gray-600 leading-relaxed\">\r\n            Precision intelligence for professionals who demand verified, source-cited reporting.\r\n          </p>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </section>\r\n\r\n      \r\n      <section class=\"py-16\">\r\n        <div class=\"container max-w-4xl\">\r\n          <h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">Our Mission</h2>\r\n          <div class=\"prose prose-lg max-w-none space-y-4 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">\r\n            <p>\r\n              ObjectWire is a verification-first intelligence platform that provides cited business and \r\n              technology analysis. We operate as a credibility engine, not a content aggregator.\r\n            </p>\r\n            <p>\r\n              Every piece of content published on ObjectWire undergoes rigorous verification using primary \r\n              sources and custom language model processing specifically trained for fact-checking and \r\n              citation validation.\r\n            </p>\r\n            <p>\r\n              Our mission is to reveal truth through transparent verification methodology and documented claims.\r\n            </p>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </section>\r\n\r\n      \r\n      <section class=\"py-16 bg-gray-50\">\r\n        <div class=\"container max-w-4xl\">\r\n          <h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-8\">What We Provide</h2>\r\n          <div class=\"grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2\">\r\n            <div class=\"bg-white p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">\r\n              <h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold mb-3\">Verified Intelligence</h3>\r\n              <p class=\"text-gray-600\">\r\n                Business and technology news with primary source citations. Every claim is documented \r\n                and verifiable.\r\n              </p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"bg-white p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">\r\n              <h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold mb-3\">Event-Driven Reporting</h3>\r\n              <p class=\"text-gray-600\">\r\n                Real-time analysis of developments affecting business, technology, and policy domains.\r\n              </p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"bg-white p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">\r\n              <h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold mb-3\">Structured Content</h3>\r\n              <p class=\"text-gray-600\">\r\n                Citation-grade content designed for integration into research and decision workflows.\r\n              </p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"bg-white p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">\r\n              <h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold mb-3\">API Access</h3>\r\n              <p class=\"text-gray-600\">\r\n                Programmatic access to verified intelligence data and structured content metadata.\r\n              </p>\r\n            </div>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </section>\r\n\r\n      \r\n      <section class=\"py-16\">\r\n        <div class=\"container max-w-4xl\">\r\n          <h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">Editorial Standards</h2>\r\n          <p class=\"text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6\">\r\n            ObjectWire maintains rigorous editorial standards to ensure the accuracy and reliability \r\n            of our reporting. All content undergoes verification using primary sources, fact-checking, \r\n            and citation validation before publication.\r\n          </p>\r\n          <a \r\n            href=\"/editorial-standards\"\r\n            class=\"inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-black text-white font-medium hover:bg-gray-800 transition-colors\"\r\n          >\r\n            Read Our Editorial Standards →\r\n          </a>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </section>\r\n\r\n      \r\n      <section class=\"py-16 bg-gray-50\">\r\n        <div class=\"container max-w-4xl\">\r\n          <h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-8\">Contact Us</h2>\r\n          <div class=\"grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3\">\r\n            <div>\r\n              <h3 class=\"font-semibold text-sm text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2\">Email</h3>\r\n              <a href=\"mailto:jack@objectwire.org\" class=\"text-lg hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors\">\r\n                jack@objectwire.org\r\n              </a>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div>\r\n              <h3 class=\"font-semibold text-sm text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2\">Phone</h3>\r\n              <p class=\"text-lg\">(575) 495-0323</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div>\r\n              <h3 class=\"font-semibold text-sm text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2\">Location</h3>\r\n              <p class=\"text-lg\">Austin, TX 78702</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </section>\r\n    </div>"
    }
